### GET all transactions

GET http://localhost:5000/transactions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <jwt token>

### GET a transaction by id

GET http://localhost:5000/transactions/97f77f85-c7b2-4164-807c-5951941de011 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <jwt token>


### Create a new transaction
POST http://localhost:5000/transactions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <jwt token>

{
  "title": "New Transaction 2",
  "description": "This is a new new new transaction",
  "amount": 300.00,
  "date": "2023-10-01T12:00:00Z",
  "category": "Food",
  "type": "expense"
}

### Delete a transaction by id
DELETE http://localhost:5000/transactions/2 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer <jwt token>

### Update a transaction by id
PUT http://localhost:5000/transactions/97f77f85-c7b2-4164-807c-5951941de011 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Authorization: Bearer <jwt token>

{
  "amount": 15.00
}

